Merge pull request #30 from snoyberg/master

Fix leaking connections snoyberg/http-client#265

Ignore IO exceptions from TLS.bye

This isn't strictly necessary for snoyberg/http-client#265, so I'm
putting it in a separate commit. It seems unlikely that anyone will be
interested in exceptions occuring when sending a disconnect message
while in the process of shutting down a connection, so I believe this is
correct behavior.
